data.description: Welcome to your turn-key, updated craftsman bungalow! This charming home is ready for you to move in and enjoy the pool! This 2 Bedroom 2 Bath is conveniently located and a short walk to the Hourglass District and Lake Como circle. The home features a spilt floor plan overlooking your backyard oasis. Enjoy the natural light coming in through the new windows. There is also plenty of storage space throughout and a storage shed. The owners have take excellent care of this home! Updates that have been completed: electrical, plumbing, 2015 roof, tank-less water heater, gutters, new paint throughout, floors, kitchen and bathroom renovations. Don’t miss out on this full of character home!!!
